{
  "stem": "4146.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We was worried, but what good is it to worry when you know you couldn't find any-- you couldn't know where they are?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or if they're still alive, or they're not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After this camp, they sent me [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Oskar Schindler.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, the Russian came near, and they were afraid that they going to catch them, and they're going kill them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they took it-- Oskar Schindler took out 1,000 men and 200 women.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This camp-- Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took it-- he wants to take us to Brunnlitz, where I show you the thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Over there they have factories, textile factories, where they rebuilt the factory for ammunition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But we have to go to Gross Rosen [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Gross Rosen we was about a couple weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Oskar Schindler took us out to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he noticed I was a a metal-- sheet metal worker and toolmaker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he needs this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ammunition.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said it when we are going there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, Oskar Schindler-- till 1943, he was an SS man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But in 1943 he changed his idea.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he knows that as the Russians come near [LAUGHS] he is not going to survive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he took the people and brought them to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we rebuild the factory for ammunition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he make the ammunition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The ammunition doesn't work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we have it just the same like in different [INAUDIBLE] barracks in camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But one thing he was doing, if you don't have food-- and his wife too-- they went, and they trade cigarettes with alcohol for food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She make it that she has a birthday, and she give everybody a half a bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
